E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Billy's got us in the shit yet again.
~z~We need to get through to the yard.
~z~Jesus, come on. This is meant to be your field of expertise. Best of luck, sport.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~天哪，来吧。这是你大显身手的地方。祝你好运，老哥。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~not quite sure I meet the dress code,
~z~I mean it wasn't enough we had to be drug dealers,
~z~I'm gonna take out Billy. Bring the bikes around so we can get outta here.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~我去干掉Billy。你们把车骑来，完事我们就走。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~You're gonna have to comp these weapons. They're needed.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~这些武器就别收钱了，征用了。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Angus, Billy's gone, man. Our chapter's dead. We got to give it a funeral.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~Angus，Billy死了，哥们。咱们帮也完了。我们办场葬礼吧。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Rush them, you fearless motherfuckes. Come on.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~干翻他们，不怕死的弟兄们。来吧。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~There's no sanctuary here William. The rules don't apply to your kind.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~这里可不是庇护所，William。那些规则在你身上并不适用。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Thanks for the advice. I'm gonna go check it out.
~z~Heads down! There's a sniper on the roof.
~z~What? You waiting for a speech or something?
~z~You never got it, did you? You never understood.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~你就没明白过，对吧？你从未明白过。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Hey Johnny, what are you in for?
~z~Dude, what the fuck, man? You're not even a cop.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~老哥，什么鬼，哥们？你又不是警察。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~I appreciate this, man. It ain't gonna be easy.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~多谢了，哥们。这次不会那么容易的。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Let the laundry guys out with the dirty uniforms.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~让这帮洗衣工把脏衣服带走。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~I'll go find Billy, boys. You get the bikes.
~z~You're not getting cash for these weapons, man. Blame Billy.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~这批家伙你回不了本了，哥们。都怪Billy。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Stay away from the gate, brothers. I'm about to blow it open with a grenade launcher.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~离门远点，兄弟们。我准备用榴弹发射器把门轰开。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~We're just here to perform some capital punishment, people.
~z~Well, we lost Terry. Another fucking casualty to Billy Grey's junkie ego bullshit.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~好吧，咱失去了Terry。又他妈是个被Billy Grey的那狗屁毒瘾害死的人。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~We're here to stop you talking William.
~z~We just wanna get the fuck outta here.

E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~真的搞笑，老哥。你又不是警察。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Let's get in there, boys. Move. Move.
~z~Well I don't doubt that, Mr. Stubbs.
~z~Bring Clay, bring all the fucking firepower you got, and meet me at the Alderney State Correctional.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~叫上Clay，手头的家伙全他妈带上。立刻来Alderney州立监狱找我。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Billy may have helped to build our club, but he sure as shit ripped it apart.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~Billy对帮派建设有所贡献，但毁也是毁在他手里。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~The rookie's here. Open the gates for him.
~z~I thought it might come to this. Wait for us, brother.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~我就寻思会发生这事。等我们，兄弟。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Go ahead... let's put this place out of it's misery.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~走吧...给这片伤心地一个解脱吧。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~I might have something to help you with it.
~z~There still guards left in this joint?
~z~You gonna roll on your brothers, Billy?
~z~You know, I would have thought your problem would be getting out, not getting into Alderney State.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~你懂的，我寻思让你伤脑筋的那个人要出来了，不在Alderney州监狱待着了。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Ain't you got rioting prisoners to worry about?
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~你们不用担心暴动的犯人了？

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~and he'll live in a condo in Arizona.
~z~to be psychos and to be greedy. You know...
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~变成疯子，变得越来越贪婪。你懂的...

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Step away from the gates.You're not on the visitor's list, you're not coming in.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~离大门远点。来访名单上没见着你，你不能进来。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Brotherhood don't mean nothing to you, Johnny.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~兄弟情谊对你来说屁都不是吗，Johnny。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Okay, brother, let's go to church one last time then.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~好了，兄弟们，那让我们最后去一次教堂吧。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~I'm amazed there are still sickos loose in this town when I look at all these freaks.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~当我看到这些奇葩的时候，我很惊讶这城里居然还有这么些怪胎。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Thinks he's going into the Witness Protection Program,
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~然后自己加入证人保护计划。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Time to move into this place. Come on.
~z~Can everyone welcome our newest recruit? Open the gates.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~有人能迎接下我们的新人吗？把门开开。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~I'm not gonna ask how you got in here, brother.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~我不会问你是怎么进来的，兄弟。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~You're getting outta here, man? Aww haven't you enjoyed your time in the State's care?
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~你要出狱了？吃国家住国家的不香吗？

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Brothers, don't let anyone in or out. Terry, Clay, we're going in.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~兄弟们，别让任何人进出大门。Terry，Clay，咱们进去。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~I'm gonna use this rocket launcher to blow the gate. Get ready!
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~我要用火箭弹炸开大门了，准备好！

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~we also had to be outlaws, to be maniacs,
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~还要做法外狂徒，做危险人物，

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~If you get into trouble, you call me when you get there,
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~要是遇到麻烦，打个电话给我，

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~You're about to have a riot on your hands.
~z~Dude, I'm sorry for spoiling the party.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~老哥，我很抱歉我打断了聚会。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~and if he collars you, you'll do fifteen years
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~万一被他得逞，你坐十五年牢，

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~You here to kick a brother while he's down?
~z~Terry, Clay, come with me. You boys hold the gate.
~z~I hate that bastard more and more every day. So long.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~我一天天的越来越讨厌这些混账东西了。再见。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~but I think I like the smoking policy.
~z~Terry, man, we got to pay our friend Billy a visit. He's been talking.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~Terry，哥们，得去拜访下咱们的朋友Billy了。他在告发。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~You boys ready? I'm about to bust this open with the rocket launcher.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~准备好了吗？我要用火箭弹轰开大门了。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Jim would tear through these bitches in a second.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~Jim一眨眼就能把这些贱逼干翻。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~I guess I just got too amped up before getting on in there. I'll see you soon.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~可能是我进去之前太激动了。再见了。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Clay, dude, we got some hard work to do. We got to pay Billy a visit in the pen.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~Clay，老哥，我们要干些重活了。咱去监狱拜访下Billy吧。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~That is not the laundry guy, boys. We have an intruder.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~那人不是洗衣工，伙计们。有人闯入。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~I'm about to introduce a pipe bomb to that gate. I hope you're all ready.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~我给大门来一发土制炸弹，你们准备好了。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~We need to get more organised. Later on.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~咱们干活得更有条理点。再见了。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, well. You're a smart guy, you'll figure something out.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~这个嘛，你可是聪明人，会想到办法的。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Give up William Grey and we'll clear off!
~z~We got what we came for, thank you.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~咱要来拿的东西到手了，谢谢。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~You got a ticket to the freak show, freshman. Freakiest freaks on earth in this pit. Good luck to you.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~新人们，你们领到的是奇葩秀的门票。地球上最奇葩的奇葩都在这深渊里了。祝你们好运。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Get away from the entrance or you will be moved.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~离入口远点，不然你们就会被抬走。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Come on man let's get outta here.
~z~Terry, dude. You got some first aid or something? Bring it here.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~Terry，老哥，你有急救用品啥的吗？拿过来。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Let's get outta here, boys. Billy stopped talking bullshit for good.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~咱们走吧，伙计们。Billy再也不会为了得到好处开口扯淡了。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Warning. Security breach: that is not the laundry guy.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~警告。安保问题：那不是洗衣工。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Alright, man. I'll take a look around.
~z~Thinks he can help pin a major drug dealing ring on you
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~准备给你和坐轮椅的兄弟扣上

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Hey, dude, you're not even a cop!
~z~Apparently he and a lot of his associates are under some serious observation.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~因为他和他的同伙都受到了严密的监视。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~The guy on the roof is down. We're cool.
~z~This gang is fucked all to hell right now, but I'll love you brothers until I die.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~虽然现在帮派彻底完了，但我会爱你们几个兄弟一辈子的。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Killing everyone around me isn't an option, Mr. Congressman. Goodbye and thank you.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~杀死我身边的人这事不是我能选的，议员先生。再见，谢谢你。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Is there a ramp you can use? Can you get hold of a guard's uniform?
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~你有没有好使的小技俩，能骗来件警卫的制服？

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Open the gate. We got the guard uniforms going out for cleaning.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~把门开开，有警卫的制服要送出去洗。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~What the fuck is left of our chapter, boys?
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~咱们分会他妈还有啥，兄弟们？

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~There's one prisoner you don't gotta worry about now.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~现在这有个囚犯你们不用操心他了。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~This is a zoo, newbie. Don't feed the animals, don't rattle the cage. You should be fine.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~这是个动物园，新来的。不要投喂动物，不要触碰笼子，否则罚款。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Can you please get back into the vehicle.
~z~hell, maybe you can jump the wall on that bike of yours. Good luck, sport.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~见鬼了，也许你可以骑你的摩托车跳墙出去。祝你好运，老兄。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~You ain't talking your way outta this, Billy.
~z~Lost MC, yeah. I'm glad I got you two with me.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~失落帮，好啊。很高兴和你俩并肩作战。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Maybe there's a disguise somewhere, or maybe you can get him from your side of the fence,
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~也许你可以在某处躲起来，或者也可以从你这边过去拿下他，

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Now, is that any way to treat a friend?
~z~Terry, man. I need some help here. Gimme first aid.
~z~You don't need to worry about that sniper no more.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~用不着再担心那个狙击手了。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~We're in the safest place in the city. Providin' there ain't a riot, that is.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~我们在城里最安全的地方，如果没有暴乱的话。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~We ain't paying for this stuff, Terry. It's being used for the Club.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~这批货就不给钱了，Terry。失落帮征用了。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Your brothers are here, William. Come and say 'hi'.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~兄弟们都来了，William。过来问个好吧。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~You brothers hold this position. Me, Terry, and Clay are gonna go get this asshole.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~你们几个守住这里。我、Terry和Clay进去找那个混蛋。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Clay wouldn't be dead if Billy had just taken his time like a man.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~要是Billy该爷们的时候不娘们，Clay就不会死了。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Man, am I happy to see you boys and these bikes.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~哥们，见到大伙们和这些摩托车，我很高兴。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Fuck if I want it standing. It stands for bullshit, nothing more.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~还不如直接解散。屁意思没有，留着干嘛。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Yeah it is. How the fuck did that happen?
~z~Dead bodies, burnt out brothers, and a clubhouse like a mausoleum.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~死的死，废的废，会所跟他妈灵堂一样。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Something's happened to the laundry van. Someone go check it out.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~洗衣房的货车有情况，来个人去检查一下。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~I told you I was good for a favor.
~z~Stay the fuck away. I just wanna kill Billy Grey.
~z~Welcome to Hell, rookie. Keep your back to the wall and your finger on the trigger.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~欢迎来到地狱，菜鸡们。背部保持靠墙，手指搭在扳机上。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Shit, if only Jim was with us now.
~z~He's dead, brothers. Now all we need to worry about is getting out of here alive.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~他死了，兄弟们。现在我们该操心的是怎样活着离开这。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~They'll either be dead or inside within a month or so.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~不出一个月就都下地狱坐大牢去了。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Terry, Clay. Thanks for rolling with me.
~z~Shit, I can't get another ticket, dude. Can I, like, suck you off or something? Come on.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，我搞不到另外的门票了，老哥。我，能不能，抱你大腿啥的？好不好嘛。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~I ain't been smugglin' nothin' into Alderney State, officer. It's all for personal consumption, man.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~警官，我可没走私东西进Alderney州，这些都是我自用的，哥们。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Oh, man. I'm thinking you're thinking we don't have a choice. We'll come meet you.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~哦哥们，我就知道你觉得咱们没得选。咱们见个面吧。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~I'm cracking the gate with a grenade, keep back boys.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~我要用手雷把门炸开，伙计们后退。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Man, I miss Jim. He was one princely son of a bitch. The best thing this gang ever had.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~天，我想Jim了。帮里就属他最高洁，他是失落帮的宝物。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~I'll forgive him the insults and injuries, but I can't forgive him that.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~我可以原谅他的冒犯中伤，但破坏帮派无法原谅。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~The laundry van doesn't look right. Get to the main gate.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~洗衣房的货车看起来不太对劲。到正门来。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~It ain't worth dying for the prisoners of Alderney State.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~为了Alderney监狱的囚犯去死不值得。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Well, Billy isn't going to be talking to anyone about us. We can clear on outta here.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~好了，Billy再也不会开口提到我们任何人了。咱们收拾收拾走吧。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~If you've learned anything at all from me, I hope it's how to cope with a crisis.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~要是你从我身上学到了啥的话，我希望是如何应对一场危机。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~not so good if you're a fucking crook.
~z~Best thing you can do - stay away from him.
~z~Shit, Terry. Bring my a first aid kit or something.
~z~Right, okay, so you're there. Use your imagination.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~对，好的，那你在这了。开动你的想象力吧。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Billy Grey sure does have a way of making mayhem.
~z~Fuck, but that van was bound to be volatile, wasn't it? Later, man.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~操，但那货车早晚会出问题，不是吗？再见吧，哥们。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~You know, I'm really lost as to what that's got to do with me, sport. I did all I could for you.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~你懂的，我真不懂这和我有啥关系，老兄。我尽力了。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Sure, man. Let me get a look at what you're talking about.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~可以的，哥们。咱们去看看你说的是啥东西吧。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~So, ummm, Stubbs. Billy's in a maximum security institution, how am I meant to do this?
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~那，呃，Stubbs。Billy可是在守卫森严的监狱啊，我该咋办？

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~I think so. You've certainly seen me naked.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~我觉得是。我都对你坦诚相待了。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Society's forgotten about these guys. We can do what we like to 'em.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~社会早就把这群人遗忘了。咱们想干啥就干啥。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Let's find this asshole and get outta here.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~找到这个混蛋，然后离开这里。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~We gotta get the uniforms cleaned. Open the gates for the laundry guys.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~我们有衣服要洗，给洗衣工开开门。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~We should regroup and hit that shit again. Sorry man, later on.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~咱得重整旗鼓再搞一波，打扰了哥们，再见。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Yo, officer, we're on the same team. I can, like, beat you off or something, but no tickets, man.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~哟，警官，咱一队的。我，能不能，把你打趴下啥的，不用门票也能进去，哥们？

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Looks like the laundry guys forgot something. Open the gates.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~看起来这帮洗衣工忘记些啥了。把门开开。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~We're just here for William Grey. Save your fucking selves.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~我们只是来找William Grey的。你们好自为之。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Someone get to the main gate. The laundry van looks suspicious.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~来人去一下正门。洗衣房的货车看起来很可疑。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Yes. Well you've got a bit of a problem there sport.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~对。这才是你的麻烦所在，哥们。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Let's go back to the house. There's one more thing we gotta do.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~回帮会所吧。还有最后一件事要做。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~You won't find salvation here, my friend. It's too late for that.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~你无法在此得到救赎，我的朋友。为时已晚。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~I don't care what happens to me as long as we get Billy. Come on.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~只要能抓到Billy，我在所不惜。来吧。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~That shit needed to be done. Billy needed to be shut up.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~攻打监狱是迫不得已，Billy必须保持沉默。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~The laundry van is back. Open up.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~洗衣房的货车回来了，开下门。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Sniper on the roof, boys. Be careful.
~z~Tell the Warden this prison's gonna burn.
~z~If these assholes kill me, promise you'll get Billy, okay?
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~就算我战死了，你们也要干掉Billy，好吗？

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Ten bucks says this asshole don't last the week.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~赌十块钱，这混蛋活不过一星期。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~The club's whole arsenal is an upsetting casualty.
~z~You can lock this place down now.
~z~We got a sniper up by that water tower. Watch out!
~z~Shit. What happened to those fucking bikes, man.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，摩托车他妈的咋了，哥们。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Sorry screws, you ain't stopping us now.
~z~You're a waste of space, dude. Get out of there.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~你活着真是浪费资源，老哥。滚吧你。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Authorised personnel only. Leave the area now.
~z~Good luck, man. You'll certainly need it.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~祝你好运，哥们。你肯定会用到的。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~You could have just come in visiting hours like all my other friends, Jonathan.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~你可以像其他人一样在拜访时间来的，Johnathan。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~My brothers, this is the last time.
~z~Keep your heads, boys. We might just survive this.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~冷静点，兄弟们。说不定能扛过这波。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Funny thing is, five years ago he woulda lead the charge into Alderney State himself.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~可笑的是，放五年前他还会亲自带队杀进监狱灭口叛徒。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~We got to clear these screws outta here or they'll take us from behind.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~必须干掉这帮杂种，不然就等着腹背受敌吧。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~which means good is never good enough.
~z~You screws are gonna die in this shithole.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~狗杂种就死在这个鬼地方吧。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~You've got the right to get the fuck out of here, man.
~z~Terry, man, I've had some bad news. Billy's been singing from his cellblock.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~Terry，哥们，有个坏消息。Billy还在牢房里活蹦乱跳的。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Intruder alert. That guy is not here for dirty laundry.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~入侵警告。那帮人不是洗衣房来的。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Let's meet Angus at the house, guys. This thing is nearly finished.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~咱们去帮会所找Angus吧，伙计们。这事快结束了。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~The new guy's here. Open the gates.
~z~You've thrown it all away, Johnny. Everything I built.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~Johnny，你把我一手建立起的东西都败光了。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~We're the bosses here now. Get out.
~z~There's a chance we might make it outta here boys. Let's fuckin' do it.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~说不定我们能活着出去，兄弟们。加油干吧。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Clear this area. It's the first of many.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~清空这片区域，这只是第一步。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Well here you are, you fork-tongued bastard. I've been looking for you.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~找到你了，狼心狗肺的混蛋。我一直在找你。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~it's that fucked up part of people
~z~How many of you assholes are on the take, huh?
~z~Hey, you two get the bikes. I'll finish things with Billy.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~喂，你俩去拿车。我跟Billy做个了结。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~That combination of greed and fucked up stupidity
~z~This place is about to descend into anarchy.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~这里就要陷入无政府状态了。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~And there's currently very large walls and armed guards between me and him.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~我和他之间可是隔了铜墙铁壁和真枪实弹啊。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Good to see you. Thanks for bringing these through.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~很高兴见到你。谢谢你把这些带过来。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Get in position. I'm cracking the door with the grenade launcher.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~各就位。我用榴弹发射器把门炸开。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~I couldn't get at Billy. He's locked down too tight.
~z~Terry, man, I'm sorry. Things got too much for me in there - I fuckin' bailed.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~Terry，哥们，我很抱歉。说来话长，我他妈开溜了。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~Get the fuck out of here, you sadistic pricks.
~z~Bad luck. You guards are standing between me and a sonofabitch I wanna kill.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~太衰了。你们这帮警卫碍着我杀那个贱逼了。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~We're here for a prisoner. Not you, guards.
E1S4AUD.translated: ~z~我们是来找囚犯的，不是你们，警卫。

E1S4AUD.original: ~z~We need to get past these fucks.
